<h3>Group Decisions Made Easy</h3>

<p>
  Want to reach agreement quickly?
  Tired of playing email ping pong again?
  Just put everybody on the same page ...
  and things will get sorted out in a snap:
</p>

<table class="decision" cellpadding="5" align="center">
  <tr class="header">
    <td>&nbsp;</td>
